                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340220-206-off1175 t18340220-206-cd1176"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18340220-206-victim1889" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
